<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,345,1533,1559]" pageId="9" pageNumber="440">Description.</emphasis>
For detailed descriptions and illustrations see 
<bibRefCitation author="Poorani, J. &amp; Booth, R. G." box="[865,1141,1533,1559]" pageId="9" pageNumber="440" pagination="56 - 68" refId="ref16643" refString="Poorani, J. &amp; Booth, R. G. (2021) Nomenclatural notes on three species of Scymnini (Coleoptera: Coccinellidae) from Ceylon. Oriental Insects, 55 (1), 56 - 68. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00305316.2020.1748134" type="journal article" year="2021">Poorani &amp; Booth (2021)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
