<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="440" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,1461,1704]" pageId="9" pageNumber="440">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1641,1667]" pageId="9" pageNumber="440">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was transferred from the genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Kugelann" authorityName="Kugelann" authorityYear="1794" box="[826,1040,1641,1668]" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Scymnus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="440" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[826,924,1642,1668]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="440">Scymnus</emphasis>
Kugelann
</taxonomicName>
to 
<taxonomicName authority="Kamiya" authorityName="Kamiya" authorityYear="1963" box="[1077,1334,1641,1668]" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Axinoscymnus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="440" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1077,1237,1642,1668]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="440">Axinoscymnus</emphasis>
Kamiya
</taxonomicName>
after examination of the 
<typeStatus box="[342,390,1678,1704]" pageId="9" pageNumber="440">type</typeStatus>
specimens by 
<bibRefCitation author="Poorani, J. &amp; Booth, R. G." box="[556,832,1677,1703]" pageId="9" pageNumber="440" pagination="56 - 68" refId="ref16643" refString="Poorani, J. &amp; Booth, R. G. (2021) Nomenclatural notes on three species of Scymnini (Coleoptera: Coccinellidae) from Ceylon. Oriental Insects, 55 (1), 56 - 68. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00305316.2020.1748134" type="journal article" year="2021">Poorani &amp; Booth (2021)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
